data.description: Your own piece of Paradise! Sitting on almost an acre, this newly renovated home is tucked away for lots of privacy, but yet so convenient to everything, including being in Harrison High School District! New flooring, freshly painted, quartz kitchen countertops, and so much more! Plenty of space with three bedrooms and a bonus room, three full bathrooms, large kitchen with plenty of cabinets and eating area, living room with Plantation shutters and stone fireplace, plus a large family room! The lower level would make a great in-law suite (or rental) with no steps from the garage to the family room, lower level additional room and full bathroom! No HOA! The house sits back off the road and on a dead end street so no through traffic! Huge backyard with shed, chicken coop, dusk to dawn safety light, plus so much space for great entertaining, room for children to run and pets! Extra large two car attached garage with plenty of room for work area, storage, etc. Great rocking chair covered front porch and deck off the kitchen. This is truly an amazing property and will be hard to duplicate!
